    <selectionEntry type="unit" import="true" name="Nemesis Claws" hidden="true" id="548a-331c-6552-54f3" sortIndex="32">
      <profiles>
        <profile name="Twisted Sadists" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="9ff3-d6d9-9679-0ac4">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s Attacks step, select an enemy unit with Suppressed X within engagement range of this unit. Then, select one of the following abilities and the selected unit gains it until the End step:


Terrifying Display: After a unit gains this ability, if one or more models from this unit died this turn, each friendly unit within 12” of and visible to this unit suffers X Suppression where X is equal to this unit&apos;s Suppressed X.


Vicious Murder: After a unit gains this ability, it suffers X+D3 SW where X is equal to this unit&apos;s Suppressed X.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <costs>
