          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">Once per battle, after this unit’s Attacks step, if one or more enemy units died this turn and there are no enemy units within 6” of this unit, you may remove this unit from the battlefield and place it into reserves.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Immaterial Predators" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="2757-8066-d4c1-db40">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit is Activated in reserves, you may roll 3D6 and select an enemy unit with Dark Gods’ Hatred. You may Deploy this unit anywhere on the battlefield at least X” away from all enemy units other than the selected unit where X is the result of that roll. If you do, this unit cannot Advance or Reposition this turn.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
