      <profiles>
        <profile name="Tormented Machine" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="eb32-7834-d67e-3298">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s End step, if this was not your second turn in a row, you may take another turn. If you do, you must select a friendly vehicle or monster unit with Wailing Spirit for activation if able.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Binding Rites" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="01f3-e58c-4544-eca7">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s End step, you may select any friendly vehicle or monster unit within 12” of this unit. Until the next time this unit is Activated, the selected unit gains Daemonic and the following ability:


Wailing Spirit: For each attack made by this unit that targets an enemy unit with Dark Gods’ Hatred, a Wound Roll of 6 causes an additional wound.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Unleash Engine" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="f5c1-8693-bf0e-c1bb">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s Select step, you may Deploy one vehicle or monster unit in reserves within 1” of this unit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
