          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit is Activated in reserves, you may ‘manifest abominations’. If you do, roll 3D6. Then, Deploy this unit anywhere on the battlefield at least X” away from all enemy units where X is the result of that roll. If you do, this unit cannot Advance or Reposition this turn.</characteristic>
