              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select an enemy unit within 14” of this unit. Until the End step, the selected unit’s Toughness is worsened by 3. If the selected unit is within 7”, its Toughness is worsened by 7 instead.</characteristic>
